# OpenAPI Generator Ignore
# https://github.com/openapitools/openapi-generator
#
# Files the generator must NOT write into the zernio/ package dir. The module
# go.mod and the curated README/reference script live at the repo root and are
# outside this output dir, so they don't need protecting here.

# No nested module file — the root go.mod covers this package.
go.mod
go.sum

# Generator scaffolding we don't ship.
README.md
.travis.yml
git_push.sh

# Generated test stubs are skip-only skeletons, and the OAS 3.1 webhooks:
# section makes the generator emit a WebhookEventsAPI test that references a
# service it never wires into APIClient (won't compile). Don't ship them.
test/**
